reviewText: The video quality makes me think that this a copy. Also there are typos in the subtitles.
I love the TV Series. I'm so happy I was able to buy it.
Good video and audio with nice subtitles as well

This is true manga in real life style. I loved the iconic manga moments that stood tall. If manga was to be in everyday life it would b close to this. The subtitles are a bit off now n then but that's OK for me. I've read some of the manga for this and it follows each other closely. I really enjoy it.
